mknutsen.graphicslibrary.graphicsobject

Class CircleGraphicObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • mknutsen.graphicslibrary.graphicsobject.GraphicObject
      • mknutsen.graphicslibrary.graphicsobject.CircleGraphicObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphicWidget
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CheckersPiece

    public abstract class CircleGraphicObject
extends GraphicObject
implements GraphicWidget
    CircleGraphicObject is a graphic object that is circular. it implements GraphicWidget so it can detect overlapping and clicks in the circle.
